<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我啊，<delay20 /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正在排練<delay8 />
自己和騎著白馬的王子，<delay20 />
初次相遇時的場景唷。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" />你看起來很開心呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是怎麼樣的場景呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><20_2 arg="4" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是王子殿下<delay20 />對我一見鍾情，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還主動向我搭話的場景唷～<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「美麗的小姐，<delay20 />要不要和我一起，<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />兩人共同打造一個王國呢？」<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就像這樣！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />原來你說的<20_2 arg="3" />白馬王子<delay frames="40" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不是比喻，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />而是指真正的王子啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這應該已經到了幻想的程度，<delay20 />
不能算是排練了吧？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然擁有夢想也很重要，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是只做這種不著邊際的夢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現實中的自己是沒辦法成長的喔？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔！<20_2 arg="4" /><pageBreak />真是的～～！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />真討厭！<delay20 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次都只會跟我說大道理，<delay8 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />這樣很無聊耶！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要問<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />一個問～題！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果<delay8 />有天你變成<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />我的話，<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會想要<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />做什麼？<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 />是<tag a="110" b="4" />！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你來得正好，那<tag a="110" b="4" /><delay8 />
也一起回答看看吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為什麼要問這個呢？<20_2 arg="1" /><delay20 />
是受到漫畫之類的影響了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想喔，<delay20 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我變成你的話<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然還是會想穿上可愛的衣服，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />站在舞台上的聚光燈下，<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
唱唱歌<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />跳跳舞吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以你也想當偶像嗎～？<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><20_2 arg="4" /><delay frames="40" />
當偶像果然是個很棒的夢想對吧？<10_4 />
<20_3 arg="8" /><delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<20_2 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="4" /></message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />我也要當偶像！</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">應該會當喜劇演員吧</message>
	<message label="103_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" />我想做自己就好！</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的假的～？<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家也太想當偶像了吧！<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還是<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />乾脆我們一起組團怎麼樣？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來組成三人偶像團體！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">如果我變成<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" /><20_2 arg="1" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個一開始的假設<delay8 />都跑哪裡去了呀？<anim id="ShyBoy" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說從現在才開始<anim id="Hello" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 />夢想當偶像嗎<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不不，<delay20 /><anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我的話還是算了吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對喔！<20_2 arg="2" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要結合<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的可愛，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />的幽默<tag a="110" b="0" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既可愛又逗趣的，<anim id="WrySmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />超～多才多藝的藝人<delay8 />
不就誕生了嗎～！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我要不要<delay20 />
乾脆來拜<tag a="110" b="4" />為師，<delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />走走看<delay8 />這個路線呢？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />如果能像你一樣，<20_2 arg="1" />這麼積極樂觀的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管想當什麼一定都會成功吧，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想要<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />做你自己就好！？<10_4 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那是什麼！<delay20 />超～酷的啦～！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你說的對！<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我才不要變成其他人！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就是要這個樣子，<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
才是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />嘛！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺我剛剛<delay20 />超～能體會的！<anim id="ColdChill" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">結果像我這樣<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><20_2 arg="1" />認真回答，<delay8 />
反而有點羞恥呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過如果你能有些體會，<delay20 />那就好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我決定<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
從今天起退出偶像界，<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
回歸做一個普通女孩的生活！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">咦？<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />怎麼了？<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />有什麼事發生了嗎？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是我在做偶像畢業公演的<delay8 />
想像練習啦～<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是總覺得<delay8 /><20_2 arg="4" />最後的結尾不夠好，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就是有種……<delay8 />
少了什麼的感覺～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在做畢業公演的<20_2 arg="3" />想像練習之前，<delay20 />
我想你應該還有很多
必須先跨越的難關才對吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等等！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><20_2 arg="4" />等一下～！<delay20 />
你的口頭禪<tag a="110" b="0" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我決定<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
從今天起退出偶像界，<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
回歸做一個普通女孩的生活！<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="5" />。<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然很搭～！<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />。<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也借你的口頭禪來用好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什麼東西<20_2 arg="3" />果然很搭呀？<delay8 />
雖然我完全搞不清楚是怎麼回事，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過你喜歡就拿去用吧<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
</msbt>